content: Controls have a tendency to freeze up and there's no zoom function, but overall this is an addictive brain-tickler.
精神時光屋,算下來一個拼圖不到一塊錢,若再加上隨機拼圖就超級物超所值,有點燒腦但只要完成一個就會有喔~的感覺,很棒 缺點就是不能放大縮小,玩到後面的方塊會蠻痛苦的,希望更新可以出放大縮小的功能

I picked this up on pc last night to calm myself down during a panic attack and it was so much better than I expected. Can't put the damn thing down now. So I grabbed it on Android as well to support the devs. Wonderful game, beautiful music, cute af dioramas.

Picross / Nonogram in 3D The music is fantastic and very chill, the controls are SPOT ON, and there are quite a few levels. It is not like the TONS of bad picross clones out there (I've tried quite a few). $5 is easily worth it (I just bought it on Switch too for $8, lol).
